query:
SELECT ts.value, ts.date, ts.regimeTag, i.nameEn, s.publisher 
FROM time_series ts 
JOIN indicators i ON ts.indicatorCode = i.code 
LEFT JOIN sources s ON ts.sourceId = s.id 
WHERE i.code LIKE '%fx%' OR i.code LIKE '%exchange%' 
ORDER BY ts.date DESC 
LIMIT 20;
